-- South Korea May Pass Law in 2010 to Create Emissions Trading, Analyst Says
-- Dinakar Sethuraman
-- 2010-06-22T03:23:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/south-korea-may-pass-law-in-2010-to-create-emissions-trading-analyst-says.html

          
          
             South Korea may pass a law this year
to create an emissions-trading market, and set targets on energy
use and greenhouse gas release for industries, C.J. Park, a
consultant to the International Emissions Trading Association,
said at a conference in Singapore today.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
